### 复杂的on condition，可抽象为a or ((b or c) and (d or e))
### 需要展开成a or (b and d or b and e or c and d or d and e)
### 等价于 a or (b and d) or (b and e) or (c and d) or (d and e)
### 对应的where condition可抽象为a and b/d and b/e and c/d and d/e is null;
